hivis.data.view

Class AbstractSeriesView<I,O>

  • java.lang.Object
    • hivis.data.DataSetDefault
      • hivis.data.AbstractDataSeries<O>
        • hivis.data.view.AbstractSeriesView<I,O>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DataListener, DataSeries<O>, DataSet, SeriesView<O>, View, Iterable<O>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    SeriesViewAppend, SeriesViewFunction, SeriesViewRow

    public abstract class AbstractSeriesView<I,O>
extends AbstractDataSeries<O>
implements DataListener, SeriesView<O>
    Base class for creating DataSeries that are optionally based on one or more other DataSeries. If input series are provided then change events on those series are forwarded to this series.
    Author:
    O. J. Coleman
